	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1> Hi, I am Ricky Li </h1>
			<p>
			I am builder and thinker working at the intersection of labor markets, technology, and socioeconomic transformation.
			</p>
			<p>
